The paper proposes a framework for autonomous car-following planning based on deep reinforcement learning, which involves artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also involves robotics (RO) and control systems (SY) as it deals with autonomous driving algorithms. Additionally, the paper uses simulation and data analysis techniques, which are commonly used in computer vision (CV) research.
